---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="At Home Plans affiliate disclosure policy — how we earn commissions and how it affects our content."
  canonicalPath="/affiliate-disclosure"
>
  <div class="container sectionPad disclosurePage">
    <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="lastUpdated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
      <p>
        At Home Plans participates in affiliate marketing programs. This means that when you click
        on certain links on our website and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission —
        at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>What Are Affiliate Links?</h2>
      <p>
        Affiliate links are tracked URLs that allow retailers and brands to know that a customer
        arrived at their site via our recommendation. When you make a purchase through one of these
        links, we earn a percentage of the sale as a referral fee.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can identify affiliate links on our site by the presence of
        <code>rel="sponsored"</code> attributes. All affiliate links open in a new tab and are
        clearly associated with the products or services we are recommending.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Which Programs Do We Participate In?</h2>
      <p>
        We may participate in affiliate programs with retailers and brands in the home decor,
        furniture, and interior design space. Our "Shop Our Picks" page and product recommendations
        within blog posts may contain affiliate links.
      </p>
      <p>
        Current and past affiliate relationships may include programs with retailers such as
        Amazon, Wayfair, West Elm, CB2, and similar home goods retailers. We will update this
        disclosure as our affiliate relationships change.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Does This Affect Our Recommendations?</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>No.</strong> We only recommend products, services, and brands that we genuinely
        believe will be useful and relevant to our audience. Affiliate relationships do not
        influence the products we feature, the content we write, or the opinions we share.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are committed to providing honest, useful interior design guidance. If we recommend
        something, it's because we think it's worth your consideration — not because we earn a
        commission.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
      <p>
        In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC) guidelines on endorsements and
        testimonials (<a
          href="https://www.ftc.gov/business-guidance/resources/ftcs-endorsement-guides-what-people-are-asking"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >16 CFR Part 255</a>), we disclose our affiliate relationships clearly and prominently.
      </p>
      <p>
        Any page or post containing affiliate links includes a notice indicating that we may earn
        a commission from purchases made through those links.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure, please
        reach out through our website. We're happy to be transparent about how we operate.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .disclosurePage {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .disclosurePage h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .lastUpdated {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .disclosurePage section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .disclosurePage section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .disclosurePage h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .disclosurePage p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .disclosurePage p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .disclosurePage strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .disclosurePage code {
    font-family: monospace;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 0.1em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .disclosurePage a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
